fields.description: Possible values: Approve, Deny, or Recommendation.  If Recommendation, then accessRecommendationsEnabled in the accessReviewSettings resource should also be set to true. If you want to have the system provide a decision even if the reviewer does not make a choice, set the autoReviewEnabled property in the accessReviewSettings resource to true and include an autoReviewSettings object with the notReviewedResult property. Then, when a review completes, based on the notReviewedResult property, the decision is recorded as either Approve or Deny.
